verse = \lyricmode {
  Then I said, \"This is what hurts me:
that the Most High God de -- serts me,
that I am from him es -- tranged
now that his right hand has changed.\"
Yet I will re -- call and pon -- der
all his awe -- some works of won -- der,
med -- i -- ta -- ting with de -- light
on his deeds so great in might.
}
